title: 9-11  (2010) (Sosich) cbr
description:
In the nebula of political and financial networks,the most improbable and unexpected meetings take place.Perilous game is played between fanatics and terrorist fundraisers,and when the playtime is over,the worst nightmare can come true!

9/11 is a geopolitical thriller which draws us into the mysteries of terrorism,secret services,multinational corporations and international finance.It's a game of pool with many strips of manipulation,greed,religious and political ideologies that irreversibly lead us towards september 11,2001.

enjoy
